4.82 OEHasSingleBond 
 
   
bool OEHasSingleBond(const OEAtomBase *atom)
    
Determine whether an atom is connected by one or more single bonds.
This function returns true if the atoms implicit hydrogen count is
non-zero.

  

  
          
     
        
